  "title": "ISic020319. ISic020319",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"xly-Grek\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xly-Grek\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΑΤΑΙΤΥΚΑΙ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΑΤΑΙΤΥΚΑΙ\">ΑΤΑΙΤΥΚΑΙ</span></span>  <span data-text=\"ε̄̓μὶ\">ε̄̓μὶ</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-transliteration\" lang=\"xly-Latn\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xly-Latn\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ataitykai emi </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"xly-Grek\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xly-Grek\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΑΤΑΙΤΥΚΑΙ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΑΤΑΙΤΥΚΑΙ\">ΑΤΑΙΤΥΚΑΙ</span></span><span data-text=\"ε̄̓μὶ\">Ε̄ΜΙ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"xly-Latn\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xly-Latn\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ATAITYKAIEMI</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic020319_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020319_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic020319.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020319-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Agostiniani 1977 (IAS I)</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Most scholars agree with the division of the text into αταιτυκαι and εμι, in which εμι would have the value of 'I am' and the second term would be an onomastic formula. Agostiniani (1977) hypothesises that this second part of the inscription could be a bimember onomastic formula (αται τυκαι), while Ferri (1968) identifies in the first part of the inscription the name Ατος, attested in Selinunte.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Ambrosini 1968 171 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002189\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002189</a></li><li> Ferri 1968 267-268 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002573\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002573</a></li><li> Lejeune 1970 181 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001880\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001880</a></li><li> Tusa 1970 248 no.131, tav.LXV <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002567\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002567</a></li><li> Agostiniani 1977 319 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002201\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002201</a></li></ul>  <ul><li> Greco 1993 201 fig.6 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002575\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002575</a></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\">  <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ι type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Μ-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Μ type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type1</a> </p> Line 1  10-12  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
